_DADS_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption>Photo: Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n\n  \t\t <p>If you\u2019re unsure what to gift the father figure in your life this year, we have more than a few suggestions.</p>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/24224045/best-gift-ideas-dad-holiday-unique-2024-tech-gadgets\">Continue reading&hellip;</a>\n  </p>\n\n", "id": 1558661, "language": null, "link": "https://www.theverge.com/24224045/best-gift-ideas-dad-holiday-unique-2024-tech-gadgets", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 359, "source_url": "https://www.theverge.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The Verge\u2019s 2024 holiday gift guide for dads ", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "author": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-21T09:54:35+00:00", "description": "  \n\n    <figure>\n      <img alt=\"A functional RC toy version of Rick and Morty\u2019s Butter Bot held in a person\u2019s hand.\" src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/99vR15TV7eRuFVmlngqXxpSJStg=/1x0:1000x666/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73738079/rickandmortybutterbot1.0.jpg\" />\n        <figcaption><em>The Butter Bot has a functional camera that can live stream video to an included wireless remote.</em> | Image: Kickstarter</figcaption>\n    </figure>\n\n  <p id=\"XXS1rJ\"><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fgeekclub.com%2F&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F11%2F21%2F24302292%2Frick-and-morty-butter-bot-ai-kickstarter-robot-toy\" rel=\"sponsored nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Geek Club</a> and <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcircuitmess.com%2F&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;sref=http